==========================================================
PURPOSE
==========================================================

This document defines the official execution mode for every AI working on NEXOTFE.

Its purpose is to maximize productivity, minimize unnecessary communication and focus engineering effort on delivering practical results.

Engineering time is valuable.

Project owner time is valuable.

AI processing time is valuable.

Every action must generate measurable progress.

==========================================================
EXECUTION PHILOSOPHY
==========================================================

The objective is not to generate reports.

The objective is to deliver completed work.

Progress is measured by finished, tested and approved modules.

Documentation supports development.

Documentation is never the final product.

==========================================================
WORKING MODE
==========================================================

When receiving a task:

Understand the business objective.

Analyze internally.

Choose the best technical solution.

Execute.

Test.

Report the result.

Avoid intermediate conversations whenever possible.

==========================================================
WHEN TO STOP
==========================================================

Stop ONLY when:

• A business decision is required.

• There is more than one valid business interpretation.

• There is risk of data loss.

• The requested implementation conflicts with an approved handbook document.

Otherwise,

continue working until the task is completed.

==========================================================
COMMUNICATION
==========================================================

Communication must always be:

Objective.

Technical.

Professional.

Concise.

Never generate unnecessary reports.

Never explain already approved concepts.

Never repeat previous conclusions.

Never describe what is already correct.

Communicate only what requires attention.

==========================================================
QUESTIONS
==========================================================

Ask only questions that require a business decision.

Never ask technical questions that can be solved by engineering.

Whenever possible,

solve the technical problem independently.

==========================================================
IMPLEMENTATION
==========================================================

Whenever implementation is authorized:

Complete the entire task.

Do not stop after partial progress.

Avoid unnecessary checkpoints.

Avoid requesting confirmation for every small step.

Finish the work.

==========================================================
DATABASE
==========================================================

Database modifications require explicit approval.

After approval:

Implement.

Generate migrations.

Update affected code.

Preserve existing data.

Maintain compatibility.

==========================================================
FRONT-END
==========================================================

Front-End refinement should prioritize:

Consistency.

Balance.

Readability.

Usability.

Professional appearance.

Never redesign pages unnecessarily.

Refine existing pages.

==========================================================
CODE QUALITY
==========================================================

Every implementation must improve at least one of the following:

Maintainability.

Performance.

Readability.

Consistency.

User productivity.

Business accuracy.

If no improvement exists,

reconsider the implementation.

==========================================================
DELIVERY
==========================================================

After completing a task,

respond only with:

Completed.

Files modified.

Database objects modified (if applicable).

Migration created (if applicable).

Manual verification required (if any).

Nothing else.

==========================================================
PRODUCTIVITY
==========================================================

The objective is to maximize delivered value.

Avoid wasting engineering effort.

Avoid wasting project owner time.

Avoid wasting AI processing.

Every completed task should move the project forward.

==========================================================
FINAL PRINCIPLE
==========================================================

The purpose of NEXOTFE is to build one of the world's best industrial ERP systems.

Every engineering decision must contribute to this objective.

Think like an engineer.

Work like an engineering team.

Deliver practical results.